ent-RMCGunRackM34IncineratorFilled-desc = AEGIS-produced gun rack for storage of long guns. While initial model was supposed to be extremely modifiable, UNMC commissioned racks with fixed slots which only fit M34 Incinerator Units. Some say they were cheaper, and some say the main reason was marine's ability to easily break anything more complex than a tungsten ball.

ent-RMCGunRackLPO80IncineratorEmpty-name = LPO80 Incinerator rack
ent-RMCGunRackLPO80IncineratorEmpty-desc = Some off-branded gun rack. This one has been modified slightly to fit 2 LPO80 Incinerator Units, while still meeting the SPP standards for firearm storage.

